1150
01:39:05,455 --> 01:39:06,247
Terima kasih, hai saudara perempuan suami!

1151
01:39:06,330 --> 01:39:09,288
Karena kamu, paspor kosongku
akhirnya mendapatkan cap visa.

1152
01:39:10,830 --> 01:39:11,908
Lihat itu!

