1238
01:43:32,577 --> 01:43:34,038
Oh! Dia telah melarikan diri...

1239
01:43:34,934 --> 01:43:35,912
Tunggu, maaf, maaf!

1240
01:43:35,992 --> 01:43:37,455
Tidak, saya hanya...Anda...

1241
